window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>If you want to build self-discipline, grow a stronger mind, gain wisdom, and boost your productivity, then pay attention....</p> <p>If you are reading these words right now, then it means you are not comfortable with your current life situation. Maybe you feel stuck or like you are not in control of your life?&nbsp;</p> <p>The good news is you made the right choice to start listening to this audiobook. If you want to change the path you are on right now, then this audiobook will guide you to a new way of life. Self-discipline is the key to everything.</p> <p>Do you want a meaningful life that everyone adores, or do you want to be just like the people you adore?</p> <p>Everyone has specific goals he or she wishes to achieve, but in order to achieve these goals, some things need to be done. If these things are not done right, it becomes challenging to get to the desired goals, and failure becomes imminent. With failure comes other struggles like sadness, lack of self-esteem, and depression. It is for this reason that people are always in pursuit of the best ways to live their lives to the fullest.</p> <p>Introducing: <i>Self Discipline: 3 Books in 1 - Mental Toughness + Stoicism + Procrastination - The Ultimate Guide to Build an Unbeatable Mind, Gain Wisdom and Increase Your Productivity</i>.</p> <p>Three manuscripts in one audiobook:</p> <p>This audiobook includes:</p> <ul> <li><i>Mental Toughness: The Ultimate Guide to Build an Unbeatable Mind, Improve Your Emotional Intelligence and Achieve Any Goal You Want</i></li> <li><i>Stoicism: The Ultimate Guide to Gain Wisdom, Resilience, Calmness and Confidence like the Great Ancient Stoics</i></li> <li><i>Procrastination: The Ultimate Guide to Beat Procrastination, Overcome Laziness, Change Bad Habits and Increase Your Productivity</i></li> </ul> <p>Here's just a glimpse of what you will learn:</p> <p><i>Mental Toughness</i>:<br> </p> <ul> <li>The importance of mental toughness</li> <li>How to set and achieve your goals</li> <li>Building an unbeatable mind</li> <li>How to become a more successful person</li> </ul> <p><i>Stoicism</i>:</p> <ul> <li>The definition of Stoicism</li> <li>Minimalism</li> <li>How to turn into a Stoic and minimalist from scratch</li> <li>Tips for families to get started with minimalism</li> <li>How parents can set examples for children to become minimalists</li> </ul> <p><i>Procrastination</i>:</p> <ul> <li>Why do we procrastinate?</li> <li>Tackling procrastination</li> <li>Getting organized</li> <li>How to clear your mind</li> <li>How to build mental strength</li> <li>Law of attraction</li> <li>Relaxation</li> <li>And much, much more!</li> </ul> <p>With this audiobook, you can begin to accomplish your tasks faster and easier while being more energetic and motivated to act on your goals and reach your full potential.&nbsp;</p>"; 
